			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">A slight modifier to pulling the Dock B people.  Head over to the Dock, stand on the hill by a lil ways from the ramp onto the Dock. Dooming Dark the closest mob, let it get to the ramp, then fear, /pet attack.  Sit and Med.
<br />
Wash Rinse Repeat.  All three of these will swim off to the left (think its west) and wont run into anything that aggros.
<br />

<br />
Running around with a SOW and DMF, ran over to Dock C, got in range of the Herald, Dark, then Fear, /Pet attack. She swims for the Nearest Island, dead about 1/2 way there.
<br />

<br />
Same or the fella that stands behind her, he doesnt Aggro when you Dark the Herald. 
<br />

<br />
Dark, then wait for him to get to the edge of the dock, or till he starts swimming towards you. Then Fear and /Pet Attack.  If you fear too early he starts walkign up the ramp instead towards the guards. The Fear would break usually before he got anywhere near enough to Agro the guards.
<br />

<br />
Also, Definitly pull towards Dock C when killing Dock A.  If you Dark/Fear Dock A where they are, they go striaght past the house and you get 3-4 others from the house heading for you.  The folks from inside the house tend to take quite a while to get them to forget you with multiple tries of Feign Death.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
